titles.title: A bill to redesignate the project for navigation, Saco River, Maine, as an anchorage area.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S3066-3067)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Environment and Public Works.
Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S7508-7511)

bill.summary:
3/13/2007--Introduced.
Redesignates a portion of the project for navigation, Saco River, Maine, as an anchorage area.
